c: 2
v: 83
t: "And when We took covenant from the progeny of Israiel: \"Do not pay obedience but to Allah, and be dutiful and kind to parents and to close relations and to the members of the weaker class and those in need. (We also advised you): “Speak fair to the people, and establish Salat and pay off Zakat\". Then you turned back except a minority amongst you and you stay aloof (of the teachings in Al-Kitab)"